OL,3,CFresh inquests ordered into McGurk's
OL,4,Cbar bombing
OL,6,FFresh inquests have been ordered into
OL,7,Fthe deaths of 15 people killed in a
OL,8,Fbomb attack on McGurk's Bar in
OL,9,FBelfast.JTwo children were among those
OL,10,Fkilled in the attack carried out by
OL,11,Fthe UVF in December 1971.JThe families
OL,12,Fof the victims believe the security
OL,13,Fforces had knowledge of the attack in
OL,14,Fadvance and could potentially have
OL,15,Fprevented it.
