OL,6,FBrenda King informed a family in the
OL,7,Fcase on Thursday that she has ordered
OL,8,Fnew inquests into the deaths.JIt comes
OL,9,Fjust days before the Government's
OL,10,FLegacy Act will halt legal proceedings
OL,11,Frelating to Northern Ireland's
OL,12,Ftroubled past.
