OL,4,Cbar bombing
OL,6,FLegacy inquests which have not reached
OL,7,Fthe point of verdict by May 1 will be
OL,8,Ftransferred to the Independent
OL,9,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,10,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).JGerard
OL,11,FKeenan, whose parents were killed in
OL,12,Fthe bomb, said: "Our families welcome
OL,13,Fthe historic decision of the Attorney
OL,14,FGeneral to direct a new inquest as all
OL,15,Fthe families have campaigned with
OL,16,Fgreat dignity for over 52 years for
OL,17,Fscraps of truth and justice from the
OL,18,FBritish state.J"Like many other
OL,19,Fbereaved families now, though, we face
OL,20,Fthe reality that the British state
OL,21,Fwill not allow this inquest to go
OL,22,Fahead as it desperately wants to stop
OL,23,Fus from discovering why our loved ones
OL,24,Fwere murdered in the McGurk's Bar
OL,25,Fmassacre and how it failed to prevent
OL,26,Fit."JSolicitor Niall O Murchu, from
